{"tid":2093230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無BNO年青人有機會去加拿大讀書","createTime":"2020-07-03T16:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T16:44:13.000Z","uid":171506,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fa7ea9cd8787aa057be4e2a8d6242e9755a3a0b9","tid":2093230,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T16:37:28.000Z","msg":"￼￼【🇨🇦加拿大Young Talents Scheme｜年輕抗爭者逃生艇】<br />\n<br />\n宣佈暫停引渡條例嘅同時，加拿大政府亦表示正考慮設立「Young Talents Scheme」，對象主要為一班香港嘅 #年輕抗爭者。<br />\n<br />\n年齡界乎18-35歲、#沒有BNO、有能力工作的香港抗爭者可申請到加拿大繼續學業，亦可以申請當地政府的學生貸款。<br />\n<br />\n《港版国安法》落實後未必能再幫忙跟進了，請大家多多留意 Hong Kong Watch的動態以了解更多詳情。<br />\n<br />\n加油，在自己崗位上好好努力，寒冬會過去的。"},{"pid":"00b0086e3b1095ade410094d276b82a1537102d7","tid":2093230,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T16:38:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/108032190900473/posts/142075840829441/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F108032190900473%2Fposts%2F142075840829441%2F&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=313a5461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/108032190900473/posts/142075840829441/</a>"},{"pid":"69682dcd328835b868a0f856d3f23df9ed5c7890","tid":2093230,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T16:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}